<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-09-04 12:14 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0407 &Cx1f; var-z
u a BC-SMART-GENES-REVIEW-2N     09-04 0298
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-SMART-GENES-REVIEW-2NDTAKE-NYT </SLUG>
  
 UNDATED: Georgetown University.  
<TEXT>
<P>
   Walters said it would be ``a plausible and morally justifiable
application of genetic techniques'' to raise the intelligence of a
