NFL kickers doing hard time this year. (Cantu, Austin
American-Statesman) Art includes 1-column mug of Cowboys kicker
Richie Cunningham.
</P>
<P>
   PAGE 3: AFC PREVIEW - Scouting reports from the 16 teams in the
AFC (Clarke, Palm Beach Post) Art includes button logos from the
AFC teams.
</P>
<P>
   WITH: AROUND THE NFL - Odds and ends column from the NFL,
featuring the best games of the season, teams that made strong
acquisitions and rookies who will make an immediate impact on their
teams. (Schlabach, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
</P>
<P>
