<HEADLINE>
 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  
   
 c. 1999 Kansas City Star  
The Kansas City Star plans to move the following stories for use by
clients of the NYTimes News Service for AMs and PMs of Sun., Sept.
5. If you have any questions, please call Melissa Moy on the Star's
News Desk at (816) 234-4720.
