   SCICIT-MUSEUM: The story will move in the ``a'' category. Story
by ERIC ADLER. It has a sidebar called SCICIT-EXHIBIT. KANSAS CITY,
Mo. _ Earlier this summer, the creators of Science City got a phone
call from a man so excited about Union Station's new science museum
that he offered a gift _ a reproduction of Sputnik, the first
satellite rocketed into outer space.
